        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'> CODING FUN WITH FOLIAX!</P><P>DOT STACKING</P><P>If Mob.DoesNotResist(yeahright)<BR>{<BR> If exists [Dot.name]<BR> {<BR>  If Dot.CasterId = CasterId<BR>    {<BR>     Dot.overwrite[Spell Slot, Spell data, CasterId, etc.]<BR>    }<BR>  else<BR>    {<BR>     Write.Buffslot[NextOpenSlot, Dot_name]<BR>    }<BR>  }<BR>Otherwise<BR>  {<BR>   Write.Buffslot[NextOpenSlot, Dot_name]<BR>  }<BR> <BR>Done. 5 minutes of psudocode... about a day's worth of work if I had the code in front of me and it works like this.</P><P>VI HIRE ME!</P><P>Foliax Pureheart <BR>Erudite Necro of the 52nd circle...<BR><img src="http://www.dabros.com/images/tlimbert/foliax.jpg" border=0><BR>MY GEAR:<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67238" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67238</a><BR></font></td>
